data.description: Unbelievable Opportunity! Seller's Special: $10,000 to Buy Down Your Interest Rate! Discover tranquility at 198 Smith Creek Rd, Denison, TX. Nestled on 4 pristine acres with stately oaks and abundant wildlife, this secluded ranch-style gem offers serene living. Enjoy 3 beds, 2 baths, a cozy living space with a wood-burning fireplace, and an open kitchen & dining area. Step onto the covered back porch and relish the solitude. A fenced backyard is the perfect space for pets to roam, but not too far! Great outdoor spaces & decks to enjoy peace and quiet under the mature trees. Embrace nature on a dead-end road, relishing the ultimate retreat with no visible neighbors.
